{"TopicId":144727,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Aircraft SAS control surface twitchy","CreatedByName":"Thingymajigy","CreatedById":136332,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-28T07:47:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Thingymajigy","CreatedById":136332,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-28T07:47:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHelp me\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/oJDLlu5.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022oJDLlu5.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/9v89uggpuzlryiq/F-15.craft?dl=1\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ECraft file\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"-DDD-","CreatedById":152222,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-28T08:05:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIMHO is a very stable design...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pecan","CreatedById":96332,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-28T16:15:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t use \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E, use trim.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlexisBV","CreatedById":81911,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-28T16:25:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would be nice if the user could tweak the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E gains in a craft-specific way (say, from an advanced menu). Right now \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E appears to use a one-size-fits-all approach, which sometimes doesn\u0027t really... fit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"foamyesque","CreatedById":2982,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-28T19:15:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you look at your control guages, the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E is applying barely any control authority; your plane is stable enough you could probably just turn it off, or, failing that, tune down your control surfaces. Looks like you\u0027ve got one of your wing control surfaces set to respond to pitch, too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Corona688","CreatedById":2511,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-28T19:36:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou could turn down the control authority on those tail fins a bit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DChurchill","CreatedById":60282,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-28T20:55:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222694989\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022144727\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221469734602\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u00222511\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Corona688\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Corona688 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou could turn down the control authority on those tail fins a bit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s what I was thinking.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}